          <div class="copy-wrapper"> 
           <p>Lay out diagrams, create flow charts, and then easily add them to other documents or embed them on a website with <a href="https://docs.google.com/drawings/?usp=mkt_drawings">Google Drawings</a>.</p> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="maia-col-6 table-bottom"> 
