          <div class="copy-wrapper"> 
           <p>Edit your profile photo, do some landscaping, create a mind map and more. Over 100 Drive apps can help you do more with your stuff. Try them by installing one from the <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/category/collection/drive_apps?hl=en_US">Drive collection</a> in the Chrome Web&nbsp;Store.</p> 
