   <section class="section-further js-hinted-fullscreen"> 
    <div class="section-centered section-centered-text"> 
     <h2 class="heading-headline">Take Drive even further</h2> 
     <div class="tabs tabs-space js-tabs" data-tab-name="space-to-play"> 
      <div class="tabs-list mobile-is-hidden"> 
       <div class="tabs-tab one-third tabs-tab-first js-activate-tab" data-tab-target="paperless"> 
        <label class="tabs-label" data-g-event="Drive" data-g-action="Tabs" data-g-label="Scan documents">Scan documents</label> 
       </div> 
       <div class="tabs-tab one-third tabs-tab-first one-third js-activate-tab" data-tab-target="offline"> 
        <label class="tabs-label" data-g-event="Drive" data-g-action="Tabs" data-g-label="Work offline">Work offline</label> 
       </div> 
       <div class="tabs-tab one-third tabs-tab-first one-third one-third tabs-tab-last js-activate-tab" data-tab-target="versions"> 
        <label class="tabs-label" data-g-event="Drive" data-g-action="Tabs" data-g-label="See old versions">See old versions</label> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="tabs-content with-select js-tab-content-container js-select-menu-container" data-select-first="true" data-select-populated="true"> 
       <!-- Mobile select menu --> 
       <div class="select-menu-wrapper select-menu-wrapper-devices"> 
        <div class="icon icon-toggle_is-active">
         &nbsp;
        </div> 
        <select class="select-menu js-select-menu"> <option class="js-select-menu-option select-menu-option" value="Scan documents">Scan documents</option> <option class="js-select-menu-option select-menu-option" value="Work offline">Work offline</option> <option class="js-select-menu-option select-menu-option" value="See old versions">See old versions</option> </select> 
       </div> 
       <div class="tabs-detail js-tabs-content js-select-menu-item" data-select-item="Scan documents" data-tab-name="paperless"> 
        <div class="maia-cols tablizer"> 
         <div class="maia-col-6 table-bottom"> 
          <div class="img-wrapper"> 
           <img src="/drive/static/images/features/tabs-4-1.jpg" alt="Example of saving docs to Drive by taking a photo with Android phone"> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="maia-col-6 table-top"> 
          <div class="copy-wrapper"> 
           <p>Scan all your paper documents with Drive for Android. Just snap a photo of documents like receipts, letters and statements – and Drive will store them instantly as PDFs.</p> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
       <div class="tabs-detail js-tabs-content js-select-menu-item" data-select-item="Work offline" data-tab-name="offline"> 
        <div class="maia-cols tablizer"> 
         <div class="maia-col-6 table-bottom"> 
          <div class="img-wrapper"> 
           <img src="/drive/static/images/features/tabs-4-2.png" alt="Google Drive offline or online switch"> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="maia-col-6 table-top"> 
          <div class="copy-wrapper"> 
           <p>Make files available offline so you can view them when your phone or tablet loses service, like on a plane or in a building with a bad connection.</p> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
       <div class="tabs-detail js-tabs-content js-select-menu-item" data-select-item="See old versions" data-tab-name="versions"> 
        <div class="maia-cols tablizer"> 
         <div class="maia-col-6 table-bottom"> 
          <div class="img-wrapper"> 
           <img src="/drive/static/images/features/tabs-4-3.png" alt="Google Drive file revision history example"> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
         <div class="maia-col-6 table-top"> 
          <div class="copy-wrapper"> 
           <p>You can look back as far as 30 days on most file types, making it easy to see who has made changes and go back to previous versions. That's file versioning made easy.</p> 
          </div> 
         </div> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
     </div> 
    </div> 
